ike":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:01:59.000Z","msg":"如果仲係兩間鐵路公司分開經營<br />\n沙中線唔會出事, 仲要一早通車<br />\n換POS visa paywave 入閘機仲洗唔洗5年丫嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bf918bcb17a1bd007f4d7baffaa70e314e8213","tid":902381,"uid":76470,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:47:58.000Z","msg":"屌那星, 講起qr code 見啲廢老用支爆寶啲電子卷黎買老麥真係火都黎<br />\n仆佢個臭街, 自己晨撚咁早撳定出黎, 到scan 咗陣已經過咗期 之後係到問點解唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再撳返出黎之後自己唔知佢自己調轉咗方向定乜柒搞到又scan唔到 總之就搞搞下, 個qr code 又過多次期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係等都等到炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好難想像搭地鐵嘅話, 前邊條友仲同你係到轉下部電話又再撳過個qr code 出黎scan 會有幾撚柒煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用QR code 比錢完全係倒退黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實最理想就係用 八記 入落apple / android pay 到用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e173c47a5e84685ad7b97ab08fb2fdee6c428fe","tid":902381,"uid":62226,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T20:42:19.000Z","msg":"到時啲中國人一定用QR code 入閘，阻住其他人入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a298cd067759f52a32163e898484d6f7300d9b13","tid":902381,"uid":57490,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"官逼民反"},{"pid":"3fa29b9f29b8c186b6cb3ac056cea30be7db4a7f","tid":902381,"uid":916,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:27:43.000Z","msg":"以後交換八達通都慳番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直接cap圖send比對方出閘就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3081bf6683b87db2d2007aff8f046dc68e6393f6","tid":902381,"uid":8478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"慘撚過支那地鐵安檢入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad63f1ba8256620d53724ffc7cf2f8ff5e00b4f","tid":902381,"uid":91638,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:32:58.000Z","msg":"有試過用qr code入機鐵既巴打都知其實唔係咁sensitivity<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都時啲大媽同OL只會由用個袋掃下掃下變左拎個moon出黎隊下隊下咁<br />\n不如八達通快啲support apple pay android pay好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fc1466d09b1acb0b227d68d8d8a7c87bdc3db9","tid":902381,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"屌那星 即係以後又多班人塞係度"},{"pid":"833329e68d931f4dbcd147e107a59d80bad4894b","tid":902381,"uid":18251,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"老老實實喺香港撘車用八達通已經喺最方便嘅方法(需然八達通公司喺仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，本地人喺無需要用其他比錢方式。<br />\n但你話每個站有一兩部(唔喺全部)方便下啲外來人又無妨嘅。"},{"pid":"8088464e4847211c4a54f38ca781566feccdc32a","tid":902381,"uid":156376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"哂鳩氣啦，係香港一定唔work，<br />\n先唔理蝗問題. 而家都已經排哂隊，<br />\n你試下用埋QR，一係唔識用，一係scan唔到，<br />\n肯撚定好多問題，無十分鐘都入唔到閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb48778f8d57085836d9ec27f5199fe683